space_reservation.space_instructions: AACC room reservations are free to reserve for AACC staff and AACC affiliated organizations. All other groups requesting AACC room reservations may be asked to pay a room reservation fee of $25/hour per room. However, all students are welcome to use and share a room with anyone else if it is not booked and during our general hours of Sundays 4pm-9pm, Mondays-Thursdays 10am-9pm, and Fridays 10am-4pm.
